## Verification

- Build: `<%= pmRunCommandPrefix %> build`
- Lint: `<%= pmRunCommandPrefix %> lint`
- Unit tests: `<%= pmRunCommandPrefix %> test`
- E2E tests: `<%= pmRunCommandPrefix %> test:e2e`
<%_ if (selectedOptionIds.includes('prisma')) { _%>
- After Prisma schema changes: `<%= pmRunCommandPrefix %> prisma:generate`
<%_ } _%>

Run the smallest relevant check first. If a change touches cross-cutting wiring, run build and tests.
